steps.name: Then  the user should be logged in and directed to the dashboard
When  the user navigates to the Claim module
And  the user clicks on create claim
And  the user selects claim type "Medical"
And  the user enters claim amount "800" and description "Health checkup"
And  the user submits the claim
Then  the claim should be successfully submitted
